    @AutoService(value=com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.BugChecker.class)
public final class HandleMethodResult
extends com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.CheckReturnValue
    An ErrorProne check which ensures that the values returned from methods are not accidentally ignored.

    This check is a substitute for CheckReturnValue. The difference is that this check ignores invocations of mutating methods on message builders.

    The check may be suppressed in the same ways as CheckReturnValue.
